summary: I saw Detective Pikachu
body:
I saw Detective Pikachu

Now, I didn’t have any prior knowledge about Pokemon going into this movie. I never played the games or anything. I had a vague idea that someone was gonna catch ‘em all but that’s more or less it.

Having now enjoyed the movie, I have a question for y'all:

Why the FUCK do they call it evolution???!!!

As anyone who has taken any evolution class ought to know, individuals do not evolve. And here’s this fucking movie going on about individual Pokemon “evolving” into better versions of themselves.

Couldn’t they have called it metamorphosis or something 😭
